## The Decision Framework

```
Start here
    │
    ▼
Do you have strict compliance needs?
(HIPAA, SOC2, GDPR with data residency, financial)
    │
    ├─ YES ──► Are tenants large enterprises paying $10k+/month?
    │               │
    │               ├─ YES ──► SEPARATE DATABASES
    │               │          (dedicated infrastructure)
    │               │
    │               └─ NO ───► SCHEMA-PER-TENANT
    │                          (isolation without full DB cost)
    │
    └─ NO ───► How many tenants do you expect?
                    │
                    ├─ < 1,000 ──► SCHEMA-PER-TENANT
                    │              (good isolation, manageable)
                    │
                    └─ > 1,000 ──► ROW-LEVEL tenant_id
                                   (or hybrid approach)
```

